title: First Sod Turned On Extra 3.9km Pipeline For Red Cliffs Irrigators (Premier of Victoria)
text: ( Source : Premier of Victoria ) Minister for Environment , Climate Change and Water Lisa Neville has turned the first sod on an extra 3.9km pipeline at Red Cliffs that will see more than 90 per cent of the district's irrigators receiving water
